data.description: **IMPROVEMENTS MADE!! The sellers have a list of items that were recently completed to make this great home even better! SUPER CUTE HOME near Beardsley Elementary School! Perfectly situated on a corner and includes two lots. Nice open floor plan with 2 bedrooms and 1 full bathroom. Feels larger than it is! You'll love the large front porch, hardwood floors, remodeled bath, screened in porch out back, 1 car garage, clean and dry basement, and the spacious open living room and dining areas. Nice size kitchen includes the gas range and refrigerator along with a newer barn sink and flooring. City water and sewer. There is a water softener in the basement, but the seller has never used it. Three portable AC units are included in the sale. **Taxes for 2023 are without exemptions. Taxes will decrease with exemptions in place. Agents, see Remarks.
